seo: seeyon,默认口令漏洞,弱口令检测,A8+企业版
seo_en: seeyon,default password vulnerability,weak password detection,A8+ Enterprise Edition
summary: 该插件用于检测Seeyon A8+系统的默认口令漏洞，尝试使用两个常见弱密码（seeyon123456和123456）登录系统，判断是否存在安全风险。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the default password vulnerability in Seeyon A8+ system. It attempts to log in to the system with two common weak passwords (seeyon123456 and 123456) to determine if there is a security risk.
